      "span_text": "To obtain neuro 2a cells stably expressing mito-RFP (a mitochondria-targeted fluorescent fusion protein) cells transfected with pIRES-puro-Su9RFP [CITATION_1] were grown in medium A containing 5 g/ml puromycin, and individual colonies were harvested and grown to mass culture."
